generation of entertainment, communications and digital technology by
partnering with entrepreneurs who have the vision, passion and tenacity to
succeed. Most investments are in the advertising, consumer, enterprise and
infrastructure sectors. By combining the best characteristics of traditional venture funds with the technical insight, scale and experience of a strategic investor, CV offers a best-in-class value proposition for entrepreneurs, portfolio companies, partnering investors, and the Comcast family of companies.  






