IT Budget




The Comcast Corporation is an American provider of entertainment, information and communications products and services. It is the largest cable company in the U.S.  The company is headquartered in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. 

NBCUniversal acquiried Dreamworks Animation; in August of 2016.  The company acquired… MoreThe Comcast Corporation is an American provider of entertainment, information and communications products and services. It is the largest cable company in the U.S.  The company is headquartered in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. 

NBCUniversal acquiried Dreamworks Animation; in August of 2016.  The company acquired the Platform in 2006 and re-branded it as Comcast Technology Solutions. 
